This project uses an Obsidian vault at `**-vault/` (obsidian-mind v6.2.1).

- **Operating manual:** `electron-agent-vault/CLAUDE.md` (read before vault operations)
- **Goals:** `electron-agent-vault/brain/North Star.md` at session start
- **Search:** QMD (`qmd --index obsidian-mind query "..."`) before reading vault files
- **Graph:** Maintain wikilinks between notes; folders group by purpose, links group by meaning
- **Skills:** See `.cursor/skills/electron-agent-vault/SKILL.md` for vault setup, graphify export, and related skills
- **Export codebase graph:** `graphify export obsidian --graph .graphify/graph.json --out electron-agent-vault/reference/graphify`

When conversation produces decisions, lessons, or project updates worth keeping, save to the vault following `CLAUDE.md` conventions.
